                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18011202-36-defend351 t18011202-36-punish188"></join>
               Confined six months in the House of Correction
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Common Serjeant.</p>
